PSCUÂ @PeopleDailyKe First Lady Margaret Kenyatta has held talks with the President of the Ford Foundation Darren Walker. The First Lady expressed gratitude to the Ford Foundation for its continued support in the Beyond Zero Initiative which has contributed to the success of the programme. She said she was looking forward to continued partnership to enable her initiative fulfil its goals of enhancing access to quality healthcare. The First Lady, who was given a tour of the organisation, is in New York to attend the ongoing 63rd Session of United Nations Commission on the Status of Women.